e":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T10:27:25.000Z","msg":"同事幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利字當頭 防疫無力 強逼勞動 你死你事<br />\n呢間銀行全部做齊<br />\n好彩已經遞左信<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n命仔緊要"},{"pid":"f85fe4cb4c5250a85a227c626d0df7d5d7fae09c","tid":1876240,"uid":251409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T11:44:58.000Z","msg":"中銀都好過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁對啲客都好無保障啦，員工同客堆埋一齊，玩真攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08a58fdef275490d66515ea9454c362ee6441c9b","tid":1876240,"uid":26961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T11:56:19.000Z","msg":"推上蘋果啦"},{"pid":"a02cbe35ab2d11096af2cd272d80559770442fbb","tid":1876240,"uid":69925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f85fe4cb4c5250a85a227c626d0df7d5d7fae09c","tid":1876240,"uid":251409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T11:44:58.000Z","msg":"中銀都好過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁對啲客都好無保障啦，員工同客堆埋一齊，玩真攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T12:20:09.000Z","msg":"個臭西政府都叫人盡量唔好外出<br />\n建行就人棄我取 人地關門大吉 我就開門吸客<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ddc0b64c432d1da16fb9d667e8985781d2e7cba","tid":1876240,"uid":11013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T12:20:38.000Z","msg":"幫推 <br />\n<br />\n唔好意思 謝一謝位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和理非 手足 家長 學生都請入黎 <b